id: pm-vxxm
title: "GH-442: lean pm contracts --summary mode for cheap agent bootstrap (25KB -> 1-3KB)"
description: "Dogfood GH-442: pm contracts costs ~25KB minimum (520KB --full) with no command+intent summary tier; add --summary for progressive disclosure. Duplicate check: pm-e2bq covers tiered HELP, pm-a22j covers measurement; no item covers the contracts-side tier."
